casebody.data:
Alexandra GRANOVSKY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Stephen A. CHAGARES, M.D., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Louis Mazzella, M.D. and Monmouth Medical Center, Defendants. C-529 September Term 2017
080017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000090-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
